    <chapter>
        <title>XML</title>
        <para>Description of XML documents purpose and meaning of its elements and atributes.</para>
        <sect1>
            <title>Purpose</title>
            <para>Purpose of this document is to capture save of an turn based strategy game.</para>
        </sect1>
        <sect1>
            <title>Elements and atributes</title>
            <para>
                <variablelist>
                    <varlistentry>
                        <term>game</term>
                        <listitem>
                            <para>Root element holding information about the game</para>
                        </listitem>
                    </varlistentry>
                    <varlistentry>
                        <term>playerOnTurn</term>
                        <listitem>
                            <para>Holds name and id of player on turn</para>
                        </listitem>
                    </varlistentry>
                    <varlistentry>
                        <term>map</term>
                        <listitem>
                            <para>Name of the current map</para>
                        </listitem>
                    </varlistentry>
                    <varlistentry>
                        <term>player</term>
                        <listitem>
                            <para>Holds information about the player and his game resources</para>
                        </listitem>
                    </varlistentry>
                    <varlistentry>
                        <term>@id</term>
                        <listitem>
                            <para>Nine character code serving as unique identificator for entity</para>
                        </listitem>
                    </varlistentry>
                    <varlistentry>
                        <term>actionQueue</term>
                        <listitem>
                            <para>Holds queue of actions that building or entity is going to perform</para>
                        </listitem>
                    </varlistentry>
                </variablelist>
            </para>
        </sect1>
    </chapter>
    
